After any significant task, update the relevant files:

| What Changed | Update These Files |
|---|---|
| Feature implemented | `progress.md`, `activeContext.md` |
| Architecture decision | `decisions.md`, `systemPatterns.md` |
| New bug or issue found | `activeContext.md` |
| Milestone completed | `milestone-timeline.md`, `progress.md` |
| Infrastructure changed | `runtime-topology.md` |
| Tool added/modified | `tool-registry.md`, `progress.md` |
